## 6 — B (CURSOR): Register / offset detail

### Authoritative layouts

**VS `VertexSlot0CB` @ b0** (`Direct3d11_ConstantBuffer.h:213-234`, `Direct3d9_VertexShaderConstantRegisters.h:28-45`):

| `lightData[i]` | c-reg | `LightData` field (D3D9) | Bytes |
|---|---|---|---|
| [0] | **c16** | `ambient` | 256 |
| [1..3] | **c17–c19** | `parallelSpecular[0]` dir / diffuse / specular | 272–304 |
| [4..5] | **c20–c21** | `parallel[0]` dir / diffuse | 320–336 |
| [6..7] | **c22–c23** | `parallel[1]` dir / diffuse | 352–368 |
| [8..23] | c24–c39 | point lights | … |
| [24..27] | **c40–c43** | `dot3` camPos / localDir / diffuse / specular | 640–688 |

| `extendedLightData[i]` | c-reg | `HemisphericLightData` field | Bytes |
|---|---|---|---|
| [0] | **c60** | `backColor` | 960 |
| [1] | **c61** | `tangentColor` | 976 |
| [2] | **c62** | `tangentMinusBackColor` | 992 |
| [3] | **c63** | `tangentMinusDiffuseColor` | 1008 |

**Correction to CONSULT-41 §5:** dot3 diffuse/spec land at **c42–c43** (`lightData[26–27]`), not c26–c27. c26–c27 are `pointSpecular[0].attenuation` / `specularColor`.

**PS `SwgVertexConstants` @ b0** (`Direct3d11_LegacyPSConstants.h:54-58`, `Direct3d9_PixelShaderConstantRegisters.h:23-27`):

| c-reg | byte offset | `PixelDot3Data` field |
|---|---|---|
| **c0** | 0 | `localDirection` (.w = spec power) |
| **c1** | 16 | `diffuseColor` |
| **c2** | 32 | `specularColor` |
| **c3** | 48 | `tangentMinusDiffuseColor` |
| **c4** | 64 | `tangentMinusBackColor` |

